text: Javlon Guseynov (born June 24, 1991) is an Uzbekistani professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Liga 1 club Borneo. ==Career== ===Borneo=== On 6 January 2019, Guseynov officially signed a year contract with Borneo. He extended the contract with Borneo on 5 January 2020. ==Honours== AGMK * Uzbekistan Cup: 2018 Individual * Liga 1 Team of the season: 2019 ==References== ==External links== *Javlon Guseynov at Soccerway Category:Living people Category:Borneo F.C. players Category:Uzbekistani footballers Category:Uzbekistani expatriate footballers Category:1991 births Category:FC AGMK players Category:Association football defenders Category:Expatriate footballers in Indonesia Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players
